    <h1>Privacy Policy for RN Chat</h1>
    
    <p><strong>Last updated: December 2024</strong></p>
    
    <p>RN Chat, developed by RN Chat, is a mobile application designed to assist users in quitting smoking. We are committed to safeguarding your privacy and ensuring the confidentiality of any information you may provide. This Privacy Policy outlines our practices regarding data collection, usage, and protection.</p>

    <h2>Data Collection and Usage</h2>
    
    <p>RN Chat is designed with user privacy in mind. It does not:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Require users to create accounts or log in.</li>
        <li>Collect any personally identifiable information.</li>
        <li>Request any permissions to access your device's data, features, or any personal information.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    
    <p>We take data security seriously. Our app is designed to function without collecting, transmitting, or storing any user data. We do not use external URLs to send or receive data. Therefore, you can rest assured that your data and privacy are safe with us.</p>

